    Verse: 13
Tags:
  - Enemy
---
When you feel yourself in the grip of an emotion such as jealousy or anger
or sorrow, detach yourself from it. Take a step back. When you do that, you
can allow the emotion to run through you without causing negative thoughts
or actions.
